t öffnen und einen wichtigen Beitrag dazu leisten können, translokale Erinnerungs- und Widerstandsräume zu etablieren.  aProjects of cultural resistance reveal dynamics of political contra-diction in a fragmented society. In the face of the current political situation, projects geared towards dialog are pressing.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aMotion pictures. 4aCultural Studies. 4aErinnerung. 4aErinnerungskultur. 4aFilm. 4aFragmentierung. 4aFriedensforschung. 4aKolonialisierung. 4aKultur. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aNahostkonflikt. 4aNahostpolitik. 4aPalästina. 4aPolitik. 4aTheater. 4aWesten. 4aWiderstand. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aColonialization.  aCultural Studies.  aCulture.  aFilm.  aFragmentation.  aMemory Culture.  aMemory.  aMiddle East Conflict.  aMiddle East Politics.  aPalestine.  aPolitics.  aResistance.  aTheatre.  aWestern World.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2017z9783110548242oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839440094zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839440094423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839440094/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2017